### Variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api
@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJlbWFpbCI6ImFkbWluQGd3YW5zaG9wLmNvbSIsInN1YiI6IjEiLCJyb2xlIjoiQURNSU4iLCJpYXQiOjE3Mjg1OTU2MDB9.example
@userId = d4da01e3-2f5a-4edf-8fa3-71f262e04eb5

### 1. Listar todos os usuários
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Obter usuário por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Atualizar usuário - Apenas nome
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "João Silva Santos"
}

### 3.1. Atualizar usuário - Apenas telefone
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "phone": "11987654321"
}

### 3.2. Atualizar usuário - Atualização completa
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "João Silva Santos",
  "email": "joao.santos@email.com",
  "phone": "11987654321",
  "role": "ORGANIZER"
}

### 4. Promover usuário para Organizador (padrão)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/promote
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "targetRole": "ORGANIZER"
}

### 4.1. Promover usuário para Administrador
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/promote
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "targetRole": "ADMIN"
}

### 4.2. Promover usuário (sem especificar role - usa ORGANIZER por padrão)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/promote
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{}

### 5. Deletar usuário (apenas ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
